7. Query to get the last Sunday of Any Month.
MariaDB [2CSE25_1690]> SELECT
    -> DATE_SUB(
    -> LAST_DAY(CURDATE()),
    -> INTERVAL (DAYOFWEEK(LAST_DAY(CURDATE())) - 1) DAY
    -> ) AS LAST_SUNDAY;
